SUMMARY:Evening Figure Drawing
LOCATION:Artspace\, 2833-A Hathaway Rd.\, Richmond\, VA 23225
DESCRIPTION:Figure Drawing sessions every second Tuesday of the month. Draw a live model for 2.5 hours. Open session\, all skill levels welcome. Must be over 18. Chairs provided\; bring your own drawing materials/board/easel.\\n\\nCost: $10 donation\\n\\nRegister: https://www.artspacegallery.org/upcoming-events/evening-figure-drawing-7xxeb-8yms9-cjrcn-te9jw-ddhg6-5jwx5-z8zbd-p2kkp-smc6z
