UID:2026-06-24-1945-unkindness-art@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260607T120501Z
DTSTART:20260624T194500
DTEND:20260624T220000
SUMMARY:18+ Figure Drawing: June Session
LOCATION:Unkindness Art\, 2923 North Avenue\, Richmond\, VA 23222
DESCRIPTION:Ongoing nude figure drawing series open to all artists 18 and over. June session is a short pose session featuring a single model — ideal for fast\, gestural sketches. Tickets required\; no door tickets. 18+ only with valid photo ID required.\\n\\nCost: $10.00\\n\\nRegister: https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-may-2026-4r4rp
URL:https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-may-2026-4r4rp
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-06-25-1800-hanover-arts@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260607T120501Z
DTSTART:20260625T180000
DTEND:20260625T203000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing Open Studio
LOCATION:Hanover Arts & Activities Center\, 500 South Center Street\, Ashland\, VA 23005
DESCRIPTION:Open figure drawing with a live model in a relaxed\, supportive environment. Artists of all levels welcome. Bring your own drawing materials\; tables and chairs provided. No registration required.\\n\\nCost: $10\\n\\nRegister: https://www.hanoverarts.net/events/figure-drawing-open-studio
URL:https://www.hanoverarts.net/events/figure-drawing-open-studio
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-07-13-1000-manchester-studios-rva@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260607T120501Z
DTSTART:20260713T100000
DTEND:20260713T173000
SUMMARY:The Alchemy Of Expression: Portrait Sculpture Workshop
LOCATION:Manchester Studios RVA\, 1300 West Main Street\, Richmond\, Virginia 23220
DESCRIPTION:Two-week portrait sculpture workshop (July 13-17 and July 20-24\, 2026). Instructed by Constance Bowden using Classical Realism methods. Covers skull anatomy\, muscles\, cartilage\, fat pads\, and portrait from life. Days 4-10 working from a live model. All materials and model fees included. All skill levels welcome. Register via Zelle to ConstanceBowden@yahoo.com.\\n\\nCost: $1600\\n\\nRegister: https://www.manchesterstudiosrva.com/upcoming-workshops
URL:https://www.manchesterstudiosrva.com/upcoming-workshops
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-07-29-1945-unkindness-art@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260607T120501Z
DTSTART:20260729T194500
DTEND:20260729T220000
SUMMARY:Drawn to Life: A Crash Course on Life Drawing
LOCATION:Unkindness Art\, 2923 North Avenue\, Richmond\, VA 23222
DESCRIPTION:All-ages crash course on life drawing covering techniques for drawing from life and the human figure. Includes a presentation\, break\, and guided figure drawing session with a live clothed model. Hosted by resident tattoo artist Liam Williams. Tickets required\; no door tickets.\\n\\nCost: $10.00\\n\\nRegister: https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/drawn-to-life
URL:https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/drawn-to-life
END:VEVENT
